snippet: A law enforcement official says an FBI agent has been detained in Pakistan after he was found to be in possession of ammunition while trying to board a domestic flight in the country....

headline.print_headline: FBI Agent Detained in Pakistan for Ammunition
headline.main: FBI Agent Detained in Pakistan for Ammunition

lead_paragraph: A law enforcement official says an FBI agent has been detained in Pakistan after he was found to be in possession of ammunition while trying to board a domestic flight in the country.
